events.name: Dream, Girl - Documentary Screening
events.description:
Sign up for free here: ga.co/2fYh3Sa

Speakers:
Rebekah Lin (Co-founder, The Social Co. SG.)
Carmen Low (Co-founder, Getai Group, Lepark, afterglowsg)
Roshni Mahtani (CEO and Founder, Tickled Media)

Partners:
Young Women's Leadership Connection
U.S. Embassy Singapore
Google Asia Pacific

We know the names of Bill Gates, Steve Jobs, and Mark Zuckerberg. But what about the female entrepreneurs? What’s their story?

From brand new startups to million dollar industries, it’s time we stop telling girls they can be anything they want to be and show them what it means to be a leader. "Dream, Girl" is the documentary showcasing the stories of inspiring & ambitious female entrepreneurs.

The panel will be moderated by Aziza Sheerin (Regional Director, General Assembly).
events.location: Google Asia Pacific HQ, 70 Pasir Panjang Road, Singapore 117371
